tournaments.name: HCS Kickoff Major Raleigh 2021
tournaments.description: Halo is back! This holiday season, Halo Infinite esports will begin at the HCS Kickoff Major Raleigh 2021! Join the Halo community as we witness returning pros and aspiring competitors from around the world throw down in Halo Infinite for the first time!
tournaments.shortDescription: Halo is back! This holiday season, Halo Infinite esports will begin at the HCS Kickoff Major Raleigh 2021! Join the Halo community as we witness returning pros and aspiring competitors from around the world throw down in Halo Infinite for the first time!
tournaments.teamPassInfo:
Live from Raleigh, North Carolina, the Halo Championship Series makes its way back to the east coast for HCS Kickoff Major Raleigh 2021! Teams from around the world will battle it out on December 17 - 19 in the first official Halo Infinite esports event ever. You won't want to miss this historic event.

A team pass includes:

  • one (1) team sign-up to play in the tournament ( a team is composed of 4 people )
  • tournament entry for four (4) competitors on the team roster
  • optionally, one (1) coach on the team roster
  • competitors and coaches are also granted General Admission access
